ShadeVil UI 1.01 Library Documentation
In Docs: 4/12 function
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<table Created_UI> ShadeVil:CreateWindow(<string> Title,<bool> IsCanAutomaticLoadTheme)
[I]: <bool> IsCanAutomaticLoadTheme is already setted to false
[EXAMPLES]: ShadeVil:CreateWindow("ShadeVil UI Library!"), ShadeVil:CreateWindow("ShadeVil UI Library!",true)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<null> ShadeVil:Theme(<Color3?> Color,<string> Type)
[I]: Sets Color for Type
[I]: Types: topbar,tabs,background,shadow,reset,text,save and load
[EXAMPLES]: ShadeVil:Theme("","Load"), ShadeVil:Theme(Color3.new(1,1,1),"topbar")
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<null> ShadeVil:Destroy(<null>)
[I]: Destroys UI
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<table Page> Created_UI:CreatePage(<string> Title)
[EXAMPLE]: Created_UI:CreatePage("Hi")
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
